text: Somehow gab.com got knocked off the web, by GoDaddy or Joyent or a combination thereof. I wanted to know how this happened, and if people agree that Gab should go, where is the line? It can't be that Nazis use their service, because Nazis use everything. I think the ACLU and the EFF should be involved here, and try to come up with some rules for all parties, so we don't have to wing this every time.
